\" /> <br />\nMc好似小獅子咁好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f8e10d260213f6f3bba4d2e1e19946ca4b75e2","tid":225400,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獅子mix老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係有啲似獅子b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aadc9e5fb3d74c9318276057bd3c351b0318574","tid":225400,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44af94071f666efc6278066f453338ba7ea300ef","tid":225400,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82Ebq3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82Ebq3Y.jpg&h=4e32a37b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n細個已經接近家貓full size<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/02/104645_310ee58f696546f6eca687e4c0b9322f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F02%2F104645_310ee58f696546f6eca687e4c0b9322f.jpg&h=7c9356f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巨爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真實睇好似熊掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f5f77cb0cda01b49006cf27fe7787c83d39430","tid":225400,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"香港應該冇貓舍，唔計鄰國最近應該係台灣，日本可能好d 但應該再貴d 同更難搵"},{"pid":"eab6f99a850613facab892a25be00aa927370f3d","tid":225400,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港應該冇貓舍，唔計鄰國最近應該係台灣，日本可能好d 但應該再貴d 同更難搵</blockquote><br />\n會搵中介，始終自己唔識呢行<br />\n但你覺得性情點？大約癡唔癡人，出爪嗰啲<br />\n我向寵物店(非pk寵物店)同佢地玩過一下，啲爪好粗壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad