sets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569a00d4091c098d3ee31048c24a467fb866d4d4","tid":225400,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"497980893f3585e150d864814e856a082a6f009f","tid":225400,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港應該冇貓舍，唔計鄰國最近應該係台灣，日本可能好d 但應該再貴d 同更難搵</blockquote><br />\n會搵中介，始終自己唔識呢行<br />\n但你覺得性情點？大約癡唔癡人，出爪嗰啲<br />\n我向寵物店(非pk寵物店)同佢地玩過一下，啲爪好粗壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中一下應該要入醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講感情嘅ja,但咁大隻下下訓落黎都幾係野<br />\n真係有心養嘅，要計下budget<br />\n中介黎講日本先係必要，台灣應該唔係必須<br />\n睇你想煩但平定比錢買簡單<br />\n<br />\n有錢有時間，真係可以去台灣睇多幾間貓舍揀貓<br />\n揀好到時搞埋針紙個d<br />\n跟你機返又得（國泰可以，港龍唔得）<br />\n趕唔切嘅寄貨運都係幾百蚊（台灣返香港，幼貓連籠唔可能過10kg嘅價）<br />\n<br />\n不過去得台灣我會建議養兩隻，可以睇埋挪威/玩具虎/布偶/孟加拉豹貓，開心好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56367d8e0dbb0f308242c4a1e59960d7014a86fb","tid":225400,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前行勝利道啲寵物店有見過<br />\n真係好撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來我以為係挪威森林，之後個店員同番我講先知係緬因貓。但唔肯定係咪純種</blockquote><br />\nCwb有間而家有幾隻，純嘅勁靚五個月已經大過普通成貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻手掌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但香港應該無乜人鍾意，見到都會驚佢賣唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/742js5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F742js5.jpg&h=b45e89bb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己覺得佢地好靚又有大手板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都覺得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個樣又霸氣成隻獅子咁<br />\n不過如果佢地會好似其他貓咁 <br />\n得閒會跳上主人大脾到坐下<br />\n咁q重主人對脾應該好快會扁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752756b636bb529158dcc1bc414102d827946d20","tid":225400,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前行勝利道啲寵物店有見過<br />\n真係好撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來我以為係挪威森林，之後個店員同番我講先知係緬因貓。但唔肯定係咪純種</blockquote><br />\nCwb有間而家有幾隻，純嘅勁靚五個月已經大過普通成貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻手掌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但香港應該無乜人鍾意，見到都會驚佢賣唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/742js5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F742js5.jpg&h=b45e89bb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己覺得佢地好靚又有大手板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都覺得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個樣又霸氣成隻獅子咁<br />\n不過如果佢地會好似其他貓咁 <br />\n得閒會跳上主人大脾到坐下<br />\n咁q重主人對脾應該好快會扁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你只練上身梗係扁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似大約4-10 kg，接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沉重的愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc711cb91fd6aa1505685418db4acffc4ee348d2","tid":225400,"uid":112909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82Ebq3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt