lass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你只練上身梗係扁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似大約4-10 kg，接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沉重的愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大大隻真係好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家屋企隻本地家貓都over 7kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf3e449077e3d72e62c18114174afd0f10968d4","tid":225400,"uid":81508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T20:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448c2748a81ea7a46065732f4f8ef1f866457938","tid":225400,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T21:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>領養啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返屋企食你嘅屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n領養有緬因你記住話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你咪養唐貓囉，<br />\n一定要養名種？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行到入愛協第一眼見到邊隻貓就領養邊隻，<br />\n咁咁先代表你有愛心呀知唔知？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申:其實我曲</span>"},{"pid":"c9bb47cfca6a7789eb9155602471f30d0434cab1","tid":225400,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T22:40:19.000Z","msg":"曲到要講自己曲真是好辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607b20319101fff3dab8088a9634fe7ac7af6be9","tid":225400,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nCwb有間而家有幾隻，純嘅勁靚五個月已經大過普通成貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻手掌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmo